From 6151087e4b1d672c244b07e11f4a70f764dfcc83 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 4 Mar 2026 15:15:39 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add GitHub Actions CI pipeline

- .github/workflows/ci.yml: runs on every push/PR to main
  - Node 20 + npm cache for fast installs
  - TypeScript type check (tsc --noEmit)
  - ESLint with react-hooks rules
  - Vite production build with placeholder env vars
  - Build output verification
- .eslintrc.json: ESLint config with react-hooks plugin
- .github/pull_request_template.md: PR checklist template
---
